      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example featuring a naturally aspirated flat-six power plant paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. This vehicle exhibits excellent mechanical health, with the engine pulling strongly through the entire rev range and the variable valve timing engaging seamlessly. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing McPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup that provides exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a fresh set of high-performance staggered tires. While the exterior shows minor road rash consistent with spirited use, the chassis rigidity and drivetrain synchronization are superb, making this an ideal candidate for the purist seeking an uncompromised analog driving experience.",
      "price": 38500.0,
